Adverse Reaction Cost=200
	~	$/Year
	~		|

Genomic Sequencing Cost=500 * EXP(-0.2 * Time)
	~	$/Year
	~		|

Mass Accrual Rate=1000 - Adverse Reaction Cost
	~	$/Year
	~		|

Mass Market Cumulative Benefit= INTEG (Mass Accrual Rate,
		0)
	~	$
	~		|

Personalized Medicine Cumulative Benefit= INTEG (Precision Accrual Rate,
		5000)
	~	$
	~		|

Precision Accrual Rate=(1000 * Treatment Efficacy Factor) - Genomic Sequencing Cost
	~	$/Year
	~		|

Treatment Efficacy Factor=1.8
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

********************************************************
	.Control
********************************************************~
		Simulation Control Parameters
	|

FINAL TIME  = 20
	~	Year
	~	The final time for the simulation.
	|

INITIAL TIME  = 0
	~	Year
	~	The initial time for the simulation.
	|

SAVEPER  = 
        TIME STEP 
	~	Year [0,?]
	~	The frequency with which output is stored.
	|

TIME STEP  = 0.25
	~	Year [0,?]
	~	The time step for the simulation.
	|

